dct_title_s: Shanghai tourist map = 上海导游图
dct_description_sm: Selected buildings are shown pictorially. On verso: Sketch map of the terminal buiding, general survey notes, and tourist information. Includes 3 ancillary maps: Shanghai Zoo -- Hongkou Park -- Yuyuan Garden. Tourist information and map of Shanghai Hongqiao Airport on verso.
dct_publisher_sm: Beijing, China : Cartographic Publishing House : Distributed by China International Book Trading Corp., 1982.
